        <b>🏘️ Kumar's Garage</b>
        <p style="color:#888; font-size:13px; margin-top:4px;">📍 Mylapore, Chennai</p>
        <div style="margin-top:6px;"><span class="tag">🚗 Car</span><span class="tag">🏍️ Bike</span></div>
